{
  "id": "6a405aa20fbc27305d001e84",
  "title": "みんなが使っているAI agentのプラン",
  "created": 1782602402,
  "updated": 1782623784,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a405aa20fbc27305d001e84",
      "text": "みんなが使っているAI agentのプラン",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782615396
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae10000000000d81554",
      "text": "のりしろ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602427,
      "updated": 1782602429
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae40000000000d81556",
      "text": "　[OpenCode Go]が$10/month",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602429,
      "updated": 1782602432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae50000000000d81557",
      "text": "　[Claude Code Pro]が$18/month",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602430,
      "updated": 1782602432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae50000000000d81558",
      "text": "　[Claude Code Max 5x]が$100/month",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602430,
      "updated": 1782602432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae50000000000d81559",
      "text": "　[Claude Code Max 20x]が$200/month",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602430,
      "updated": 1782602432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ae50000000000d8155a",
      "text": "　いずれにせよ[OpenCode Go]が一番安いのか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602430,
      "updated": 1782602432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405adf0000000000d81553",
      "text": " みんなが使っている[Claude Code]のプランはどれなんだろう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602424,
      "updated": 1782602439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000589c2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405af20000000000d8155b",
      "text": "Claude Code",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602444,
      "updated": 1782602446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000ae8947",
      "text": " $18/month pro[caki.icon][基素.icon][nomadoor.icon][はるひ.icon][taktamur.icon][Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782618940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000e121bf",
      "text": "  まだkimi全然つかってないけど体感opencode goでkimiができる作業のほうがclaude proでできる作業よりもやや多い印象",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000aff85d",
      "text": "  weekly limitがきびしすぎる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000ceadb8",
      "text": "  codexと両方契約してる。頻繁にlimitが来るので次は5xかな...[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000b1c485",
      "text": "   https://chatgpt.com/ja-JP/codex/pricing/",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f00000005e06a8",
      "text": "   CodexもGoがあるんだ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f00000006a5016",
      "text": "    coding agent使うなら、3000円/月以上のプランが必須？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000ee7825",
      "text": "   来月はcodexにしてみようかなと思ってる[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000bff4a1",
      "text": " $100/month Max 5x[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782618945
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f0000000c15d75",
      "text": " \tproだと足りないのが鬱陶しいので、お高いがしゃーなしと判断した",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f00000006135a5",
      "text": " \t基本会話と調べ物ばかりだからか、足りてる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f000000042b4d6",
      "text": " $200/month Max 20x[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782618950
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f00000005047b9",
      "text": "  複数社複数プロジェクトを全部自分でやるのでこれでもキツイ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f000000040b11d",
      "text": "  ソフトウェア開発会社だったら逆に複数人チームでやるからPro(Team)で済むとかあるのかな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405aca1280f000000022096c",
      "text": "  \tEnterprise使ってるけど上限なし従量課金っぽくて、モニタリング超大事[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602402,
      "updated": 1782602402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405af80000000000d8155c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782602449,
      "updated": 1782603477
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ed500000000007de477",
      "text": " 普通のチャットのclaudeのプランとclaude codeのプランとで違うの？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782603477,
      "updated": 1782603590
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4063ab00000000009eb379",
      "text": " \t両者の区別はなくプランとして無料、Pro(17$)、Max(100$と200$)がある[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782604716,
      "updated": 1782604832
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4063b200000000009eb37a",
      "text": "\t \tClaude Codeが使えるのはProから。つまり無料プランではClaude Codeが使えない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782604723,
      "updated": 1782604754
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4063f000000000009eb37b",
      "text": "\t \tProの5倍使えるMax 5xが100$、20倍使える20xが200$",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782604785,
      "updated": 1782604954
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4064a100000000009eb37e",
      "text": "\t \tだが業務でエージェントバリバリ動かしてると20xでも全然足りないので、上限なしの従量課金ができるTeams/Enterpriseプラン（業務用プラン）にする",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782604962,
      "updated": 1782604993
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ed200000000007de475",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782603474,
      "updated": 1782603474
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405ed200000000007de476",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782603474,
      "updated": 1782603474
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405af80000000000d8155d",
      "text": "Codex",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782602449,
      "updated": 1782602451
    },
    {
      "id": "6a408c5e0000000000b70400",
      "text": " ￥3000/month plus[wogikaze.icon][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782615135,
      "updated": 1782621938
    },
    {
      "id": "6a40a6f5000000000057c904",
      "text": "  Claude使えないときの保険[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782621941,
      "updated": 1782621976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a40a8d300000000005374a1",
      "text": "   保険にしてはかけすぎでは？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782622379,
      "updated": 1782622388
    },
    {
      "id": "6a40a8dc00000000005374a2",
      "text": "   保険程度ならOpenCode Goのほうがreasonableそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782622388,
      "updated": 1782622400
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4069240000000000607f62",
      "text": " ￥16800/month pro 5x[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782606117,
      "updated": 1782618916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a405afa0000000000d8155e",
      "text": "",
